        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR2a0001-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_027-45a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:05:53.903+09:00">运行到哪一宿，该宿的分野国就吉利。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_027-45a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:08:30.147+09:00">按推算位直该留在某宿而没有留在那里，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_027-45a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:03:51.909+09:00">或者已经离开某宿后又返回该宿并停留在那里，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_027-45a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:04:13.497+09:00">填星就是土星。以和斗宿的距离确定它的位直。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_027-45a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:04:20.222+09:00">它主持中央，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_027-45a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:04:31.27+09:00">五行中属土，掌管夏末，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_027-45a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:04:38.779+09:00">日期千支戊己，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_027-45a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:04:42.762+09:00">是中央黄帝，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_027-45a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:04:49.698+09:00">执掌德行，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_027-45a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:04:53.936+09:00">为女主的象征。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_027-45a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:05:03.618+09:00">土皇约二十八年在恒星间运行一周，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_027-45a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:05:12.53+09:00">所以一年镇守一宿，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_027-45a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:07:15.101+09:00">所当分野国能</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_027-45a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:07:19.23+09:00">获得领土，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_027-45a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:07:31.113+09:00">或者得到女子。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_027-45a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:08:55.257+09:00">或者刚刚留在那里</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_027-45a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:09:33.648+09:00">很快又向东或向西离开了那里，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_027-47a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:17:53.767+09:00">失次落后两三宿就叫缩，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_027-47a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:18:00.518+09:00">所当国的王后有悲成之事，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_027-47a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:18:08.423+09:00">这一年可能丧命，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_027-47a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:20:50.418+09:00">要不这个国家将发生天崩地动的大灾难。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_039-30a.34" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:23:30.883+09:00">"太子所以这样干，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_039-30a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:23:39.277+09:00">就是因为我和英齐的缘坟。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_039-30a.36" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:23:46.106+09:00">我们母子愿意逃避到别的国家去，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_039-30a.37" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:23:55.339+09:00">或及早自杀，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_039-30a.38" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:24:07.254+09:00">不要让我们母子日后被太子作鱼肉宰割。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_039-30a.39" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:24:18.112+09:00">当初您说要庭掉他，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_039-30a.40" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:24:41.838+09:00">我还觉得遗憾；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_039-30a.41" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:24:45.904+09:00">事到如今，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_039-30a.42" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:25:22.226+09:00">我才知道我错了。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_124-9a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:31:40.935+09:00">但他运气好，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_124-9a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:31:45.134+09:00">每次碰到危难，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_124-9a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:32:49.571+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_124-9a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:33:35.256+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_124-9a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:34:42.636+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_076-14a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:46:07.561+09:00">赵玉的主意还没有拿定，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_076-14a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:46:11.43+09:00">刚好楼缓从泰国来了。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_076-14a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:46:51.508+09:00">于是赵王就和楼</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_076-14a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:46:58.161+09:00">缓商量说。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_076-14a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:47:09.038+09:00">" 割地给泰国还是不割地给泰国，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_076-14a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:47:36.345+09:00">你看哪个好?"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_076-14a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T11:47:46.595+09:00">楼缓推辞说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_076-14a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-08T12:05:39.731+09:00">"这不是我所应该回答的。"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_083-18a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-09T14:04:01.714+09:00">谚语说..</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_083-18a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-09T14:04:10.797+09:00">有的人交往了一辈子还像刚认识一样，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_083-18a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-09T14:04:33.221+09:00">有的人刚认识就像老朋友一样。"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_083-18a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-09T14:04:41.817+09:00">为什么呢?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_083-18a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-09T14:05:31.712+09:00">关键在于是否两心相通做到真正了解。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_000-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T18:32:13.486+09:00">黄帝</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_000-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T18:32:18.467+09:00">是少典氏的后代，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_000-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T18:32:27.632+09:00">姓公孙，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_000-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T18:32:36.631+09:00">名轩拔。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_000-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T18:32:52.008+09:00">轩幸在刚生下来就显出与众不同的灵异，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_000-1a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T18:33:00.442+09:00">几个月就会说话，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_000-1a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T18:34:14.357+09:00">三五岁就表现出思维敏捷，反应很快，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_000-1a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T18:34:27.449+09:00">少年时代非常勤勉，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_000-1a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T18:34:44.649+09:00">成年以后识辨力很强。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_001-3a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T18:36:10.695+09:00">当轩辗还是诸侯时，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_001-3a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T18:36:19.842+09:00">神农氏的统治逐渐衰弱，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_001-3a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T18:36:28.715+09:00">诸侯之间互相侵伐，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_001-3a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T18:37:43.805+09:00">祸害百姓，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_001-3a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T18:37:50.199+09:00">而神农氏无力讨伐。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_001-3a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T18:38:46.928+09:00">于是轩辗就动用武力</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_001-3a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T18:39:31.586+09:00">去讨伐那些不守纪律、不来朝拜神农氏的人，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_001-3a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T18:39:40.19+09:00">因而诸侯都对他表示臣服与追随。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_001-3a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T18:39:49.891+09:00">而安尤最凶暴，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_001-3a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T18:43:27.119+09:00">没有人能够制服他。</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
